Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.18,0:00:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everyone, Kaleido Star is about to start!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.15,0:00:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When watching Kaleido Star,\Nplease keep the room brightly lit,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.90,0:00:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and sit as far from the TV as you can.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.11,0:00:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm Sora Naegino.\NI came to America all by myself{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.69,0:00:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}with aspirations of joining Kaleido Stage.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.50,0:00:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everything is new to me, {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.17,0:00:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but I'm doing my best in the spirit\Nof "try it rather than think about it."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.68,0:00:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's nothing I can't do if I try,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.93,0:00:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and if I can do it without\Ntrying, that'll be super lucky.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.73,0:00:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And if I'm gonna do it, I just\Ngotta do it! Gotta! Gotta! That's me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.57,0:00:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, well, well, does everyone\Nknow the story of "The Little Mermaid"?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.27,0:00:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's a really wonderful story. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.90,0:00:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This time, I attempt to get the leading part,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.86,0:00:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but I make a mistake and\Nhave a really scary experience.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.28,0:00:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And I can't get it out of my mind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.57,0:01:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh! I've really found myself\Nin a pinch this time! I have! I have!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.05,0:01:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What is it that you want to do? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.65,0:01:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Every time I was asked that {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.50,0:01:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I looked up at the blue sky {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.29,0:01:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The answer is only in my heart {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.59,0:01:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't easily say the\Nwords that are really important{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.12,0:01:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I start running towards\Nthe place the light points to{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.16,0:01:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's so much in my heart\Nthat I want to embrace, I could cry{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.32,0:02:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll keep painting my way,\NI promise, take it someday{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.26,0:02:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Beyond the horizon,\Nwhere the white clouds drift{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.31,0:02:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The future is lined up and\Nit'll always be there by my side{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.21,0:02:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.01,0:02:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I brought you lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.29,0:02:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Marion.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.84,0:02:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, it's time for lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.27,0:02:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.46,0:03:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we sit here today?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.26,0:03:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm going to read you the\Nstory of "The Little Mermaid" today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.12,0:03:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Once upon a time,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.47,0:03:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there was a very beautiful mermaid princess."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.94,0:03:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"My Amazing Challenge For the Lead Role."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.09,0:03:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for coming to\Nsee us at Kaleido Stage today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.98,0:03:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Due to stage equipment maintenance,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.43,0:03:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the performance of Cinderella\Nwill be suspended for two weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.15,0:03:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We look forward to when\Nyou come visit us again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.95,0:03:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great work, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.37,0:03:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally, the vacation that we've\Ndreamed of will start tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.72,0:03:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do the two of you have any plans?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.70,0:03:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.81,0:03:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be ready for the audition.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.42,0:03:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.32,0:03:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's going to be an audition\Non the last day of vacation...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.80,0:04:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, you don't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.91,0:04:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't. No, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.30,0:04:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Why am I the only one who doesn't know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.52,0:04:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It should be posted on \Nthe dorm bulletin board.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.96,0:04:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! So, what's posted?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.53,0:04:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since last summer's\Nperformance was so popular,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.25,0:04:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they're going to stage it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.77,0:04:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Little Mermaid"!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.89,0:04:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.48,0:04:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Oops.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.70,0:04:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.00,0:04:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've only seen this on video!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.68,0:04:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I can't believe this! Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.44,0:04:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get to see the real thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.79,0:04:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.90,0:04:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a real tear jerker, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.94,0:04:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially at the end,\Nwhen the Little Mermaid
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.50,0:04:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,jumps off the ship into the ocean!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.02,0:04:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll make you cry a river no\Nmatter how many times you see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.93,0:04:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.34,0:04:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since Miss Layla is going to try\Na new swing maneuver this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.05,0:04:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the cast auditions seem mainly for\Npeople who are good on swings too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.06,0:04:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.28,0:04:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is your chance, Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.81,0:04:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.52,0:04:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your specialty, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.31,0:04:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it my specialty?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.36,0:04:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, you're the one who\Nmastered the Golden Phoenix.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.91,0:04:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.67,0:04:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You could get the\Nsupporting role right off the bat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.48,0:04:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.98,0:04:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I will make a serious effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.39,0:04:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You could get a raise while you're at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.42,0:04:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.94,0:04:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll get chauffeured to\Nand from work every day!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.94,0:04:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if I should be spoiled so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.10,0:05:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.15,0:05:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's already acting like\Nshe's passed the audition.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.22,0:05:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like, she makes me sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.77,0:05:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"So, in order to get a human\Nbody, the Little Mermaid..."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.99,0:05:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.48,0:05:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.37,0:05:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is the preparation\Nfor the production going?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.48,0:05:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is going smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.47,0:05:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.60,0:05:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, since I'm busy,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.22,0:05:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see the performance right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.49,0:05:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The audition is scheduled\Nto be held in two weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.97,0:05:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.24,0:05:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see it right this minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.43,0:05:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can't see it right now,\NI will call the whole thing off!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.06,0:05:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, if you would settle for only my\Nscene, I could show you right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.08,0:05:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you displeased with me for some reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.37,0:05:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you're a wonderful star\Nand I'm very aware of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.63,0:05:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, don't you have\Nany stars other than Layla?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.04,0:05:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's so nasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.02,0:06:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's like the sea witch \Nin the Little Mermaid.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.90,0:06:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, how about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.68,0:06:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This will be a special\Naudition in front of a client.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.09,0:06:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you successfully complete this audition,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.64,0:06:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you will be given the part of\Nthe Little Mermaid on the spot,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.81,0:06:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and you will play the\Nleading role in this production.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.04,0:06:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, if you fall, the Little Mermaid\Nperformance will be cancelled.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.51,0:06:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anybody who will\Naccept this challenge even then?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.08,0:06:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said if she falls,\Nthe show will be cancelled.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.12,0:06:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like, super bad and risky.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.99,0:06:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't there anybody\Nwho'll accept this challenge?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.89,0:06:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you take this opportunity\Nto try for the part of the Little Mermaid?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.45,0:06:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the leading part. The leading part!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.09,0:06:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? The leading part, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.87,0:06:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh-ho...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.80,0:06:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.46,0:06:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That settles it then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.97,0:06:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, play the part of the\NLittle Mermaid right this minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.10,0:06:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.88,0:06:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But isn't the Little \NMermaid Miss Layla's role?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.81,0:06:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.19,0:06:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said you were good\Nat swings just a while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.37,0:06:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sounded like, so confident.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.14,0:06:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.11,0:06:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you said if you got the part,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.53,0:06:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you'd get them to raise \Nyour pay by ten times.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.93,0:06:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.52,0:07:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And buy a tropical island...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.12,0:07:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.12,0:07:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.28,0:07:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you've planned that far ahead,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.18,0:07:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll really have you play\Nthe part of the Little Mermaid.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.74,0:07:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.93,0:07:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.72,0:07:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is everything ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.85,0:07:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.79,0:07:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ken, what do I need to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.69,0:07:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.41,0:07:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll explain the details of\Nthe performance to you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.26,0:07:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From where you're standing now,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.67,0:07:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you just need to use that swing
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.02,0:07:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to jump to the swing on the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.06,0:07:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I press the buzzer, jump out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.22,0:08:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then your timing will match with the\Nswing on the other side of the waterfall.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.67,0:08:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What waterfall?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.68,0:08:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.13,0:08:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.39,0:08:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.93,0:08:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.17,0:08:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.22,0:08:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.45,0:08:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're starting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.50,0:08:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.34,0:08:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you'll be able to pull it off, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.50,0:08:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you tell me not to worry, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.33,0:08:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't see the other side because\Nof the waterfall. What am I gonna do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.07,0:08:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, let's just give it a try\Ninstead of thinking about it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.44,0:08:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.51,0:08:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, too late! Come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.63,0:09:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good, I can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.20,0:09:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.43,0:09:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What? I didn't make it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.51,0:09:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's over... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.70,0:09:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good, you're awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.18,0:09:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You saved me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.09,0:09:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.23,0:09:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From the look of it, you should be fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.63,0:09:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.26,0:10:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll be leaving now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.40,0:10:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.51,0:10:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.12,0:10:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our castle, Kaleido Stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.71,0:10:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.30,0:10:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You cannot come this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.60,0:10:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.49,0:10:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.71,0:10:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.48,0:10:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You cannot come to our world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.52,0:10:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should go back to\Nthe world that you belong to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.96,0:10:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.30,0:10:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait! Wait! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.35,0:10:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.22,0:10:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, she came to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.15,0:10:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you seem okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.25,0:10:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.64,0:10:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still have them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.42,0:10:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.53,0:10:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch! Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.12,0:10:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, you should still take it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.79,0:10:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They said that you dislocated\Nyour shoulder just a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.71,0:10:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if Mr. Yuri hadn't been there,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.31,0:10:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you would've suffered a lot\Nmore than a dislocated shoulder.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.14,0:10:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.15,0:10:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri rescued you in the nick of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.37,0:11:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd never seen real mouth-to-mouth\Nresuscitation before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.69,0:11:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So that wasn't a dream. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.00,0:11:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, and then, when Ken saw that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.18,0:11:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah, Ken got...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.00,0:11:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Ken got...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.20,0:11:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.60,0:11:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.48,0:11:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.24,0:11:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't "What?" me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.27,0:11:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't push yourself, Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.92,0:11:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The doctor still doesn't want\Nyou to do anything, remember?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.98,0:11:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.36,0:11:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't show Mr. Kenneth\Nthat I can do this soon,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.27,0:11:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they'll cancel the show.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.82,0:11:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Huh? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.61,0:11:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Huh? What's wrong?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.22,0:11:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Huh? What? Huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.45,0:11:44.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something's wrong... Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.02,0:11:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wha... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.25,0:11:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora. Sora. Can you hear me, Sora?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.47,0:11:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What just...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.69,0:11:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, you have to take it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.26,0:11:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.02,0:12:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think today's not a good day for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.45,0:12:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go home and rest for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.30,0:12:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.67,0:12:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.74,0:12:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to be honest with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.24,0:12:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, could it be that you're afraid?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.67,0:12:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that it after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.59,0:12:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, if you're afraid...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.35,0:12:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.24,0:12:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mind me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.52,0:12:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop her right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.86,0:12:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.54,0:12:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.33,0:12:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.39,0:12:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.80,0:12:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, how was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.03,0:12:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the time being, I was able to\Ntalk him into giving us another chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.77,0:12:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rest is up to the performer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.96,0:12:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.13,0:12:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.92,0:13:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The dining room will be closing soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.01,0:13:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't eat,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.25,0:13:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you won't be able to heal quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.86,0:13:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.13,0:13:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How truly pitiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.96,0:13:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.56,0:13:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you skip today's practice?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.86,0:13:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm injured, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.77,0:13:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why won't you come out of there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.47,0:13:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My shoulder hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.86,0:13:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Why?\N--Who cares anyway? Just leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.81,0:13:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, it is the same as that other time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.01,0:13:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That other time?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.25,0:13:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once, there was a man\Nwho was able to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.10,0:13:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That man also became\Nunable to jump due to injuries,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.30,0:13:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for he was not able to overcome\Nthe fear of when he injured himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.85,0:13:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was he able to appear on stage?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.67,0:13:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.69,0:13:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.78,0:13:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did he overcome his fear?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.64,0:13:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So as I thought, your shoulder\Ninjury has nothing to do with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.68,0:13:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind that!\NHow did he do it?! Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.62,0:13:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.76,0:13:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Hanged Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.62,0:13:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.53,0:14:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if you want to change your current situation,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.59,0:14:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you cannot just keep running away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.11,0:14:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not running...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.90,0:14:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The man gradually became unable to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.85,0:14:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.04,0:14:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.90,0:14:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.01,0:14:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ken...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.18,0:14:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.80,0:14:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew you'd come, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.56,0:14:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ken, I'm sorry about what I said earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.44,0:14:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.98,0:14:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It didn't bother me at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.77,0:14:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, you're going to do it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.27,0:14:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Practice, I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.09,0:14:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.75,0:14:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got things ready because\NI figured you'd be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.39,0:14:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got things ready... You mean this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.66,0:14:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.18,0:14:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For your practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.20,0:14:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.57,0:14:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.88,0:14:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I wasn't being\Nconsiderate of your feelings earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.54,0:14:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no. I should apologize to you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.68,0:15:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But don't you think these swings\Nare too low to provide good practice?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.64,0:15:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I want you to gradually build your\Nsuccesses starting from a low height
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.64,0:15:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and get you to picture\Nthe perfect image of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.49,0:15:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The perfect image?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.13,0:15:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.22,0:15:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it over and over
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.22,0:15:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,until the image of falling\Nis erased from your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.81,0:15:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But still, don't you think\Nthis height is just too easy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.05,0:15:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we'll see about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.84,0:15:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.23,0:15:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do something like this, Ken!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.67,0:15:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is all for the sake\Nof your image of success.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.28,0:15:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.69,0:15:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll coordinate the timing,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.49,0:15:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so jump when I give you the signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.42,0:15:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you ready, Sora? Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.49,0:15:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about the time you made a mistake,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.29,0:15:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and just focus on\Nsynchronizing with the sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.65,0:15:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.83,0:15:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready? One, two, three!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.55,0:16:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right, Sora?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.35,0:16:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. I'm sorry, Ken.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.10,0:16:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.01,0:16:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, be strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.51,0:16:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.34,0:16:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.16,0:16:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please trust me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.58,0:16:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll lead you to success, I promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.84,0:16:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't rescue you heroically like Yuri did,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.42,0:16:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'll make sure to\Nmake you the Little Mermaid!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.30,0:16:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.19,0:16:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Thank you, Ken.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.42,0:16:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.03,0:16:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.07,0:16:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.17,0:16:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is a Kung Fu Master, Master Linn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.36,0:16:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master knows a breathing\Ntechnique for mental concentration,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.39,0:16:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so you should learn it\Nand improve your focus.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.09,0:16:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.47,0:16:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't whine, just do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.14,0:17:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Master Linn is\Nsaying he wants to test you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.03,0:17:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.26,0:17:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He says if you can keep up with him,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.41,0:17:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he'll teach you the technique\Nfor mental concentration.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.40,0:17:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.41,0:17:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't be too hard on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.38,0:17:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.38,0:17:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.23,0:17:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He says you passed the test.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.68,0:17:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Already?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.17,0:17:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.16,0:17:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a deep breath and calm your emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.88,0:17:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.75,0:17:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One more time...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.95,0:17:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do it right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.44,0:17:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.44,0:18:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master Linn says that he is\Nvery satisfied with your progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.04,0:18:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.75,0:18:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the technique \Nof mental concentration!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.36,0:18:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're amazing, Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.61,0:18:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe he's going\Nto teach you that technique!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.98,0:18:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.37,0:18:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, hurry up and do what he's doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.68,0:18:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.19,0:18:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be one with nature and\Nresign yourself to nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.98,0:18:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you will be the wind,\Nthe water, and the earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.82,0:18:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Abandon yourself and be\None with your surroundings.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.34,0:18:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is indeed the secret\Nof mental concentration.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.21,0:18:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.70,0:18:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Resign myself to nature... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.85,0:18:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to take a little break?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.74,0:18:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.59,0:18:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'm almost there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.14,0:19:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I think you should\Nbe ready to do this soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.80,0:19:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But maybe I should do a\Nlittle more rehabilitation before...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.53,0:19:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The doctor's told me that you're\Nalready completely recovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.29,0:19:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you're afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.95,0:19:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're saying that you can't jump,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.62,0:19:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there's no point in you being here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.31,0:19:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's no point in you being here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.61,0:19:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.83,0:19:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.66,0:19:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.06,0:19:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.96,0:19:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've worked hard all this time practicing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.38,0:19:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.76,0:19:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I could do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.39,0:19:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I probably won't be able to do\Nanything when it really counts.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.97,0:19:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't jump anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.05,0:19:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.39,0:19:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll probably never jump again!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.91,0:20:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you're never going to\Njump for the rest of your life?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.33,0:20:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still remember how I felt when I learned
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.08,0:20:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that I would never be able to\Njump because of my weak heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.73,0:20:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't jump even if I want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.64,0:20:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you're the same now, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.28,0:20:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the truth is you {\i1}can {\i0}jump.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.82,0:20:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you were practicing the Golden Phoenix,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.51,0:20:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wondered how you could jump so happily
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.94,0:20:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when the practice was so tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.06,0:20:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are many good\Nperformers at Kaleido Stage,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.96,0:20:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you're the first one who made me wish
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.42,0:20:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that I could jump like that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.09,0:20:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember how it feels\Nwhen you're jumping, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.82,0:20:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How it feels when I'm jumping...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.35,0:20:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give up, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.55,0:20:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want my Sora to\Nbe defeated by her fears.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.84,0:20:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.44,0:21:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Ken.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.72,0:21:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.35,0:21:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A blindfold? Will she be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.16,0:21:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.66,0:21:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.86,0:21:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.82,0:21:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.16,0:21:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.74,0:21:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.08,0:21:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Sora. One, two, three!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.49,0:21:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you're saying that you can't jump,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.19,0:21:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}there's no point in you being here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.04,0:22:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Be one with nature and\Nresign yourself to nature.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.64,0:22:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Be one with your surroundings. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.23,0:22:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then, you shall be the sky,\Njust as you were named.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.51,0:22:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.04,0:22:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You did it, Sora. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.25,0:22:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You really are the most radiant\Nperson at this Kaleido Stage.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.23,0:22:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When you're lonely, what do you do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.91,0:22:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Never say you don't get any of that{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.25,0:22:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sleep, play, flip through a magazine{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.10,0:22:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When you're lonely, you're lonely{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.55,0:22:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Like always, invisible vibes fly\Naround the city today, tulututu{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.30,0:22:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Anyway, the vector of my heart\Nis talking about so many reasons{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.81,0:23:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to be free and fly the skies{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.65,0:23:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I don't have space to spread my wings{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.38,0:23:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I have faith {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.42,0:23:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There is a future yet to be shaped{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.16,0:23:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And there's a me that I want to shape{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.84,0:23:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if I'm sad, even if it's a mistake{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.30,0:23:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll do what I want and\Nfly towards the freedom{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.68,0:23:36.64,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Next Kaleido Star"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.97,0:23:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Go, Sora! You're the leading lady!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.23,0:23:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And so, this is my first leading role.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.40,0:23:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I tried performing it\Nperfectly like Miss Layla, but...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.83,0:23:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Fewer people are coming to see us...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.60,0:23:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And the sponsor doesn't like it either.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.57,0:23:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, what in the world am\NI doing wrong? What? What?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.52,0:23:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Next time on Kaleido Star,\N"Facing An Amazing Wall."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.23,0:23:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My wings are my dream\Nand on towards the sky...{\i0}
